Filter Public Catalog

Source: R/aaa.R
public_filter.Rd

Filter Public Catalog

Usage

public_filter(endpoint = c("dataset", "api", "csv"), title = NULL)

Arguments

endpoint

<chr> API endpoint; options are "dataset" (default), "latest", "api", "csv"

title

<chr> dataset title to search for; use NULL to return all

Value

<tibble> of search results

Examples

public_filter(
  endpoint = "dataset",
  title    = "Medicare Fee-For-Service  Public Provider Enrollment")
#> # A tibble: 1 × 8
#>   title          modified   temporal   accrualPeriodicity identifier describedBy
#>   <chr>          <date>     <date>     <chr>              <chr>      <chr>      
#> 1 Medicare Fee-… 2024-10-16 2023-01-01 [R/P3M] Quarterly  https://d… https://da…
#> # ℹ 2 more variables: description <chr>, landingPage <chr>

public_filter(
  endpoint = "api",
  title    = "Medicare Fee-For-Service Public Provider Enrollment : 2024-09-01")
#> # A tibble: 1 × 5

#>   <chr>                             <date>     <date>     <chr>     <chr>       
#> 1 Medicare Fee-For-Service Public … 2024-10-16 2024-09-30 https://… https://dat…
